			<div class="content" id="post-content-2340883">
									

<p>Wow, I didn't even add the tags yet. Glad you liked enough to +1. Yeah, I decided to try to add as many layers as I could find of extra info.</p>
<p>The way I think of it is an auditory(as well as with the other senses) version of how some animals can see colors that are not in the visible spectrum of light that humans can see. Similarly memetics and info hazards are just info that is outside the visible spectrum, but moves deeper into people's minds so that it is compulsory.</p>

