<p>Thanks! Well if you think about it, having someone(s) in the Foundation who discovered kill words and the defensive memetics which are supposed to guard so much documentation means they can probably create lots of other stuff too. They're sort of like IT except for everyone's brains. I want to see how this goes, but I hope to add a couple other tales in the same vein.</p>
