<p>Yeah, a lot of the drawbacks you note are part of the style I drew from, which I like but can see how people find them annoying. I was trying for not just &quot;You're a wizard Harry!&quot; but &quot;Wait, there are how many wizards? And all they're supposed to do is fly around and play quid ditch?' What else are they up to?&quot;</p>
